---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import EmailCapture from '../components/EmailCapture.astro';
---

<Layout title="Take Action" description="Join the fight for a Denver that works for everyone. Here's how you can help right now.">
  <section class="hero-mini">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 data-en="Take Action" data-es="Actúa">Take Action</h1>
      <p data-en="This movement only works if people show up. Here's how you can fight for Denver right now." data-es="Este movimiento solo funciona si la gente participa. Así puedes luchar por Denver ahora mismo.">
        This movement only works if people show up. Here's how you can fight for Denver right now.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="action-list">
        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">1</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Sign Up for Updates" data-es="Suscríbete para Recibir Actualizaciones">Sign Up for Updates</h3>
            <p data-en="Join our email list. We'll send you policy updates, action alerts, and ways to get involved. No spam, just organizing." data-es="Únete a nuestra lista de correo. Te enviaremos actualizaciones de políticas, alertas de acción y formas de participar. Sin spam, solo organización.">
              Join our email list. We'll send you policy updates, action alerts, and ways to get involved. No spam, just organizing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">2</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Join the Signal Group" data-es="Únete al Grupo de Signal">Join the Signal Group</h3>
            <p data-en="Our real-time organizing happens on Signal. Coordinate actions, share resources, connect with other Denver organizers. Encrypted and secure." data-es="Nuestra organización en tiempo real sucede en Signal. Coordina acciones, comparte recursos, conéctate con otros organizadores de Denver. Encriptado y seguro.">
              Our real-time organizing happens on Signal. Coordinate actions, share resources, connect with other Denver organizers. Encrypted and secure.
            </p>
            <a href="https://signal.group/#CjQKIDnsKXfjsfzF6z51cdXSTRKzZWxG71JNlmN-lawMNOkWEhAKQ8yueN1JU8E6RaRM6D8I" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--secondary" data-en="Join Signal Group" data-es="Únete al Grupo de Signal">Join Signal Group</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">3</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Call Your Councilmember" data-es="Llama a Tu Concejal">Call Your Councilmember</h3>
            <p data-en="Pick an issue from our platform. Call your district's councilmember. Tell them what you want. It takes 2 minutes and it works - they track every call." data-es="Elige un tema de nuestra plataforma. Llama al concejal de tu distrito. Diles lo que quieres. Toma 2 minutos y funciona - registran cada llamada.">
              Pick an issue from our platform. Call your district's councilmember. Tell them what you want. It takes 2 minutes and it works - they track every call.
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.denvergov.org/Government/Agencies-Departments-Offices/Agencies-Departments-Offices-Directory/Denver-City-Council/Council-Members-Websites-Info" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--secondary" data-en="Find Your Councilmember" data-es="Encuentra a Tu Concejal">Find Your Councilmember</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">4</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Show Up to City Council" data-es="Asiste al Concejo Municipal">Show Up to City Council</h3>
            <p data-en="Denver City Council meets every Monday at 5:30 PM. Public comment is open. Show up. Speak. Record it. Post it. When 20 people show up demanding rent control, they notice." data-es="El Concejo Municipal de Denver se reúne cada lunes a las 5:30 PM. Los comentarios públicos están abiertos. Asiste. Habla. Grábalo. Publícalo. Cuando 20 personas se presentan exigiendo control de alquileres, lo notan.">
              Denver City Council meets every Monday at 5:30 PM. Public comment is open. Show up. Speak. Record it. Post it. When 20 people show up demanding rent control, they notice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">5</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Share Our Policy Proposals" data-es="Comparte Nuestras Propuestas Políticas">Share Our Policy Proposals</h3>
            <p data-en="Read a policy you like? Share it on Reddit, social media, group chats, your neighborhood Nextdoor. Every share reaches someone new." data-es="¿Leíste una política que te gusta? Compártela en Reddit, redes sociales, chats grupales, el Nextdoor de tu vecindario. Cada vez que la compartes, llega a alguien nuevo.">
              Read a policy you like? Share it on Reddit, social media, group chats, your neighborhood Nextdoor. Every share reaches someone new.
            </p>
            <a href="/platform" class="btn btn--secondary" data-en="Browse the Platform" data-es="Explora la Plataforma">Browse the Platform</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">6</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Volunteer Your Skills" data-es="Ofrece Tus Habilidades como Voluntario">Volunteer Your Skills</h3>
            <p data-en="We need: translators (especially Spanish), data analysts, graphic designers, writers, canvassers, legal expertise, social media managers, and anyone willing to knock on doors." data-es="Necesitamos: traductores (especialmente español), analistas de datos, diseñadores gráficos, escritores, promotores, experiencia legal, gestores de redes sociales y cualquiera dispuesto a tocar puertas.">
              We need: translators (especially Spanish), data analysts, graphic designers, writers, canvassers, legal expertise, social media managers, and anyone willing to knock on doors.
            </p>
            <a href="https://forms.gle/g9hhjj7ekhnpK5hA8" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--primary" data-en="Volunteer Sign-Up" data-es="Inscripción de Voluntarios">Volunteer Sign-Up</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item action-item--highlight">
          <span class="action-item__number">7</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Demand Flock Cameras Off" data-es="Exige que Apaguen las Cámaras Flock">Demand Flock Cameras Off</h3>
            <p data-en="Denver's Flock cameras photograph 2 million vehicles per month. ICE searched this data over 1,400 times. City Council voted 12-0 to reject the contract. Mayor Johnston bypassed them. Call the mayor's office at (720) 865-9000 and your councilmember. Tell them: turn off the cameras, respect the council vote, and pass a surveillance oversight ordinance." data-es="Las cámaras Flock de Denver fotografían 2 millones de vehículos al mes. ICE buscó estos datos más de 1,400 veces. El Concejo Municipal votó 12-0 para rechazar el contrato. El alcalde Johnston los eludió. Llama a la oficina del alcalde al (720) 865-9000 y a tu concejal. Diles: apaguen las cámaras, respeten el voto del concejo y aprueben una ordenanza de supervisión de vigilancia.">
              Denver's Flock cameras photograph 2 million vehicles per month. ICE searched this data over 1,400 times. City Council voted 12-0 to reject the contract. Mayor Johnston bypassed them. Call the mayor's office at (720) 865-9000 and your councilmember. Tell them: turn off the cameras, respect the council vote, and pass a surveillance oversight ordinance.
            </p>
            <a href="/platform/public-safety" class="btn btn--secondary" data-en="Read Our Surveillance Policy" data-es="Lee Nuestra Política de Vigilancia">Read Our Surveillance Policy</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">8</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Push State Legislators on Rent Control" data-es="Presiona a los Legisladores Estatales sobre Control de Alquiler">Push State Legislators on Rent Control</h3>
            <p data-en="Colorado state law (C.R.S. 38-12-301) bans all local rent control. Denver cannot cap rents until this preemption is lifted. The repeal bill (HB 23-1115) passed the House but died in the Senate by one vote. Contact your state senator and representative. Tell them to repeal the ban or support a ballot initiative. Governor Polis opposes repeal -- a ballot measure goes directly to voters and bypasses his veto." data-es="La ley estatal de Colorado (C.R.S. 38-12-301) prohíbe todo control de alquiler local. Denver no puede limitar alquileres hasta que se elimine esta restricción. El proyecto de derogación (HB 23-1115) pasó la Cámara pero murió en el Senado por un voto. Contacta a tu senador y representante estatal. Diles que deroguen la prohibición o apoyen una iniciativa de votación. El gobernador Polis se opone a la derogación -- una medida en la boleta va directamente a los votantes y evita su veto.">
              Colorado state law (C.R.S. 38-12-301) bans all local rent control. Denver cannot cap rents until this preemption is lifted. The repeal bill (HB 23-1115) passed the House but died in the Senate by one vote. Contact your state senator and representative. Tell them to repeal the ban or support a ballot initiative. Governor Polis opposes repeal -- a ballot measure goes directly to voters and bypasses his veto.
            </p>
            <a href="https://leg.colorado.gov/find-my-legislator" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--secondary" data-en="Find Your State Legislator" data-es="Encuentra a Tu Legislador Estatal">Find Your State Legislator</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">9</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Demand a State Surveillance Oversight Law" data-es="Exige una Ley Estatal de Supervisión de Vigilancia">Demand a State Surveillance Oversight Law</h3>
            <p data-en="Colorado has no law requiring city council approval before police acquire surveillance technology. California's AB 481 requires legislative body approval for all surveillance acquisitions -- Colorado needs the same. This would have prevented Mayor Johnston from bypassing the council on Flock. Contact your state legislators and demand a Colorado CCOPS (Community Control Over Police Surveillance) bill." data-es="Colorado no tiene una ley que requiera la aprobación del concejo municipal antes de que la policía adquiera tecnología de vigilancia. La AB 481 de California requiere la aprobación del cuerpo legislativo para todas las adquisiciones de vigilancia -- Colorado necesita lo mismo. Esto habría evitado que el alcalde Johnston eludiera al concejo sobre Flock. Contacta a tus legisladores estatales y exige un proyecto de ley CCOPS de Colorado.">
              Colorado has no law requiring city council approval before police acquire surveillance technology. California's AB 481 requires legislative body approval for all surveillance acquisitions -- Colorado needs the same. This would have prevented Mayor Johnston from bypassing the council on Flock. Contact your state legislators and demand a Colorado CCOPS (Community Control Over Police Surveillance) bill.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-item">
          <span class="action-item__number">10</span>
          <div>
            <h3 data-en="Support Denver Charter Reform" data-es="Apoya la Reforma de la Carta de Denver">Support Denver Charter Reform</h3>
            <p data-en="Denver's strong-mayor system lets the mayor veto council legislation with only 4 of 13 votes needed to sustain the veto, sign contracts just under review thresholds, and deploy surveillance without a vote. We need charter amendments to: lower the veto override threshold from 9 to 8 votes, require council approval for all surveillance contracts regardless of dollar amount, lower the $500,000 contract review threshold, and require council confirmation of key cabinet appointments. These changes require a ballot measure -- talk to your neighbors about why Denver's power balance is broken." data-es="El sistema de alcalde fuerte de Denver permite al alcalde vetar la legislación del concejo con solo 4 de 13 votos necesarios para sostener el veto, firmar contratos justo por debajo de los umbrales de revisión y desplegar vigilancia sin votación. Necesitamos enmiendas a la carta para: bajar el umbral de anulación de veto de 9 a 8 votos, requerir aprobación del concejo para todos los contratos de vigilancia independientemente del monto, bajar el umbral de revisión de contratos de $500,000 y requerir confirmación del concejo para nombramientos clave del gabinete.">
              Denver's strong-mayor system lets the mayor veto council legislation with only 4 of 13 votes needed to sustain the veto, sign contracts just under review thresholds, and deploy surveillance without a vote. We need charter amendments to: lower the veto override threshold from 9 to 8 votes, require council approval for all surveillance contracts regardless of dollar amount, lower the $500,000 contract review threshold, and require council confirmation of key cabinet appointments. These changes require a ballot measure -- talk to your neighbors about why Denver's power balance is broken.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <EmailCapture />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-mini {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-mini h1 { color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero-mini p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; }

  .action-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .action-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .action-item__number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .action-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .action-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .action-item--highlight {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    border-width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg-card) 0%, #f0fafa 100%);
  }

  .action-item--highlight .action-item__number {
    background: #c53030;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .action-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
